snippet.title: Orbit Quest: Agon Space Station
snippet.description:
Welcome to the deadly Agon Space Station in Orbit Quest. Word of advice please avoid the lasers they have a 95% death rate. 

Find out more about the video game Orbit Quest at http://frostlabstudios.com/ 

And follow us on twitter https://twitter.com/frostlabstudios?lang=en

Also be the first to try our game at Play NYC!
